prompts.frontCover:
Minimalist flat 2D illustration for a humorous birthday greeting card front. A clean white background with plenty of negative space. In the center, a cartoon illustration of a young couple from the waist up. A young East Asian man with short black hair and a big, happy smile is hugging a young East Asian woman from behind. The woman has long, straight black hair parted in the middle, wears thin-rimmed round glasses, and is also smiling warmly. He is wearing a simple tan hoodie. She is wearing a simple light blue crewneck sweatshirt. Above them, in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script, is the single word "birthday". The overall style is clean, simple, with an elegant and lighthearted feel.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
